long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stay up to date with Omani royal decrees and ministerial decisions by downloading the Decree Alerts Chrome Extension. 

This app displays the latest royal decrees and ministerial decisions published on Decree without having to visit the website.
